t", "text": ", see 1. You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ilay h`*aA", "text_ar": "اِلَي هٰذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA A_irobuka", "text_ar": "مَا اـِرْبُكَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[the reason of]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thy want of this?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA liY", "text_ar": "مَا لِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiyhi A_irbN", "text_ar": "فِيهِ اـِربٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I have no want of it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) By"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gayori", "text_ar": "غَيْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uwliy AlA^arobapi", "text_ar": "اُولِي الاَرْبَةِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Kur [xxiv. 31], are meant"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Idiots;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "persons deficient in intellect:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_irobapN", "text_ar": "اـِرْبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as meaning “intelligence:”] (Sa'eed Ibn-Jubeyr, S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "not such as have need of women."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Jel.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA HafaAwapN", "text_ar": "لَا حَفَاوَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA^arabapN", "text_ar": "مَاَرَبَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, A,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA HafaAwapN", "text_ar": "لَا حَفَاوَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA^orabN", "text_ar": "مَاْرَبٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M,) is a proverb, (S, A,) meaning He only honours thee"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for the sake of something which he wants"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of thee;"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "not for love"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of thee: (A, Meyd:) or only thy"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "want"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "brought thee;"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "not"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "the object of"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "paying extraordinary honour"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to me. (M.) [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov., ii. 690.] You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mina AlA^aroDi", "text_ar": "مِنَ الاَرْضِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aloHiqo bimaA^orabika", "text_ar": "اَلْحِقْ بِمَاْرَبِكَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Go thou whither thou wilt [so as to attain thy want"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "T", "S", "M", "A", "Msb", "TA", "Meyd"]}, {"entry_id": "n525", "headword_ar": "اَرِبٌ", "root": "Arb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ariybN", "text_ar": "اَرِيبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". ―         -b2-  Also ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Expert; skilful:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ariba", "text_ar": "اَرِبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", of which it is the part. n.:) or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "accustomed to,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "practised"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "exercised in, a thing, and knowing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "skilful."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA.) See also 1, in the latter part of the paragraph.       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aribN bi$aYo 'K", "text_ar": "اَرِبٌ بِشَىْ ءٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ilay $aYo'K", "text_ar": "اـِلَي شَىْءٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (see"}, {"kind": "arabic